data.description: Enjoy One Level living in this cute 3 bedroom ranch home.  With a huge living room/dining room area open to the kitchen.  The kitchen has lots of cabinet storage for the cook in the family to store all your kitchen small appliances and cookware.  The Owners suite is also HUGE (16X17.6) with his/her closets.  The master bath has double sinks, separate shower and soaking tub.  New Roof (2019) New HVAC (2019 No City Taxes! Come see it today!
